      <title>花旗银行反击纽约网络欺诈诉讼：我们不是“坏人”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/citi-pushes-back-on-ny-s-online-fraud-suit-we-re-not-bad-guys</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团表示，如果纽约州赢得诉讼，指控该公司在防止网络欺诈方面做得不够，美国银行将被迫在电子支付处理方式上做出“重大转变”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/citi-pushes-back-on-ny-s-online-fraud-suit-we-re-not-bad-guys</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 19:02:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OpenAI 与 Hearst 达成协议，将新闻内容引入 ChatGPT</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/openai-hearst-strike-deal-to-bring-news-content-to-chatgpt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OpenAI 和赫斯特通讯公司 (Hearst Communications Inc.) 达成协议，将该出版商的杂志和报纸内容引入聊天机器人 ChatGPT，这是该人工智能初创公司与媒体公司签署的一系列合作协议中的最新一项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/openai-hearst-strike-deal-to-bring-news-content-to-chatgpt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 16:49:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 在华盛顿峰会上大力宣传芯片的能源效率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/nvidia-touts-energy-efficiency-of-chips-at-summit-in-washington</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面对人们对人工智能计算电力需求的担忧，英伟达公司在周二华盛顿举行的会议上大力宣传其最新芯片的能源效率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/nvidia-touts-energy-efficiency-of-chips-at-summit-in-washington</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本田有意修改电动汽车战略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/honda-leaves-door-open-to-revise-ev-strategy-amid-slower-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本田汽车公司表示，如果纯电动汽车的需求持续减弱，它愿意改变其电气化路线图，这表明该日本汽车制造商最终可能加入国际同行的行列，放弃电动汽车目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/honda-leaves-door-open-to-revise-ev-strategy-amid-slower-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 为广告商推出生成式 AI 视频工具</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/meta-launches-generative-ai-video-tools-for-advertisers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 正在推出新的人工智能工具，帮助广告商更轻松地制作和编辑视频，以期吸引那些花更多时间观看视频的 Facebook 和 Instagram 用户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/meta-launches-generative-ai-video-tools-for-advertisers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Northvolt 在下一次财务测试中面临 2800 万美元的税单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/northvolt-faces-28-million-tax-bill-in-next-test-of-finances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[10 月 14 日，Northvolt AB 将面临 2.87 亿瑞典克朗（2800 万美元）的税单，这可能是这家资金短缺的电池制造商在其旗下一家子公司破产后面临的下一个财务障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/northvolt-faces-28-million-tax-bill-in-next-test-of-finances</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 14:57:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Verizon 为收购 Frontier 举债 100 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/verizon-lines-up-10-billion-in-debt-for-frontier-acquisition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Verizon Communications Inc. 已获得 100 亿美元的短期银行资金，用于资助其收购 Frontier Communications Parent Inc.。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/verizon-lines-up-10-billion-in-debt-for-frontier-acquisition</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 14:53:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冲突加剧，以色列主要机场客流量下降 43%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/israel-s-main-airport-sees-43-drop-in-traffic-as-conflict-rages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于 10 月 7 日的袭击和随后的冲突导致航空公司撤出或减少从该枢纽起飞的航班，特拉维夫本·古里安国际机场的乘客数量在 2024 年前 9 个月下降了 43%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/israel-s-main-airport-sees-43-drop-in-traffic-as-conflict-rages</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 13:59:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Temu 瞄准亚马逊 Fire TV 流媒体设备，推出售价 4 美元的遥控器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/temu-targets-amazon-fire-tv-streaming-products-with-4-remote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Temu 与亚马逊公司 (Amazon.com Inc.) 陷入激烈竞争，其目标是这家电子商务巨头最受欢迎的产品线之一：Fire TV 流媒体设备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/temu-targets-amazon-fire-tv-streaming-products-with-4-remote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Northvolt 子公司因扩张计划受阻申请破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/northvolt-unit-files-for-bankruptcy-as-swedish-expansion-paused</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Northvolt AB 为旗下的一个子公司申请破产保护，以限制这家陷入困境的电池制造商在瑞典北部暂停扩张所带来的财务影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/northvolt-unit-files-for-bankruptcy-as-swedish-expansion-paused</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 07:23:13 GMT</pubDate>
